info.title: Speak & Math
info.description: Recordings of a Circuit-Bent Texas Instruments Speak & Math.

setttings.fftsettings: 256 64 512 for melbands and spectral shape, 256 64 256 for everything else except when analyzing the whole sample in which case it's 1024 128 1024
setttings.descriptors: mean of loudness, deriv of loudness, mean of centroid, deriv of centroid, mean of flatness, deriv of flatness, mean of pitch, pitch confidence, 40 melbands (for spectral compensation), 13 mfccs + stats
setttings.comment: 8d of descriptors for nearest neighbor matching, and then loudness and 40 melbands for loudness/spectral compensation and 13 mfccs + stats for classificaiton/regression. also includes normalized and robust scaled versions of each set of data and time frame
